l=\"noopener noreferrer\">WordPress development company<\/a> to build a website instead of doing everything yourself. While WordPress started to design blogs, it has now moved up the level to build enterprise websites and portals. With thousands of plugins and the availability of themes, WordPress has opened up a world of new horizons for a large audience.<\/p>\n<p>If you are wondering how large the WordPress ecosystem is. This infographic will build the context for WordPress development. <a href=\"https:\/\/w3techs.com\/technologies\/overview\/content_management\/all\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener nofollow noreferrer\">W3 Techs says<\/a> WordPress empowers around 32% of websites.<\/p>\n<p>WordPress enhances a website content management system by facilitating <a href=\"https:\/\/www.hiddenbrains.com\/e-commerce.html\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">e-commerce solutions<\/a>, <a href=\"https:\/\/www.hiddenbrains.com\/blog\/amazing-multi-vendor-marketplace-platforms-for-your-ecommerce-store.html\">multivendor marketplace<\/a>, ERP, website analytics solution, SEO solutions. It allows bringing together different types of plugins, themes, and core features.<\/p>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Understand_your_Business_Needs\"><\/span>Understand your Business Needs<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p>Before you start WordPress development, you first need to identify your need and identify top <a href=\"https:\/\/www.hiddenbrains.com\/hire-wordpress-developers.html\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">WordPress developers<\/a> if you don\u2019t even know what you want from them? Outline your exact needs and some things you consider include:<\/p>\n<ul style=\"margin-left: 30px;\">\n<li>Objective and goal of your website?<\/li>\n<li>What type of website do you want to create?<\/li>\n<li>Whether a site is an online store or a <a href=\"https:\/\/www.forbes.com\/sites\/forbestechcouncil\/2018\/10\/23\/how-to-use-wordpress-as-a-saas-platform\/#a5e70d68effb\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener nofollow noreferrer\">SaaS platform<\/a>?<\/li>\n<li>What features do you need your website to have?<\/li>\n<li>Do you want to purchase a pre-built theme or create a custom theme?<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-6798\" src=\"https:\/\/www.hiddenbrains.com\/blog\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/10\/Why-Use-a-WordPress-Development-for-Business.jpg\" alt=\"Why Use a WordPress Development for Business\" width=\"908\" height=\"4220\" srcset=\"https:\/\/www.hiddenbrains.com\/blog\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/10\/Why-Use-a-WordPress-Development-for-Business.jpg 908w, https:\/\/www.hiddenbrains.com\/blog\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/10\/Why-Use-a-WordPress-Development-for-Business-768x3569.jpg 768w, https:\/\/www.hiddenbrains.com\/blog\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/10\/Why-Use-a-WordPress-Development-for-Business-600x2789.jpg 600w, https:\/\/www.hiddenbrains.com\/blog\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/10\/Why-Use-a-WordPress-Development-for-Business-300x1394.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 908px) 100vw, 908px\" \/><\/p>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Copy_the_code_to_include_this_detailed_Infographic_of_%E2%80%9CWordPress_Development_for_your_Business_Site%E2%80%9D_on_your_blog_or_page\"><\/span>Copy the code to include this detailed Infographic of &#8220;WordPress Development for your Business Site&#8221; on your blog or page:<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<pre>&lt;img class=\"size-full wp-image-5984 aligncenter\" src=\"https:\/\/www.hiddenbrains.com\/blog\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/10\/Why-Use-a-WordPress-Development-for-Business.jpg\" alt=\"WordPress Development for your Business Site\" width=\"908\" height=\"4338\" \/&gt;<\/pre>\n<div id=\"ez-toc-container\" class=\"ez-toc-v2_0_47_1 ez-toc-wrap-left counter-hierarchy ez-toc-counter ez-toc-transparent ez-toc-container-direction\">\n<div class=\"ez-toc-title-container\">\n